Psychology of them recovered: Why do we spend more money? 
The participants of the auctions are prone to spend more money and to overrate the product. 
The neurologists and economists of the University of new York discovered the neurological bases - economic of this apparently irrational and known conduct. 
According to the study appeared in the magazine Science, the people does not want to lose in competences as the auctions of eBay, therefore prefers to pay even one excessive price. 
The scientists tried to establish the neurological plan of this "play" through experimental auctions. 
One of the groups of volunteers played lottery, the other participated in an auction and in the meantime the system of functional magnetic resonance was examined by means of (fMRI) the active zones of the brain of the participating people in the experiment. 
In both play they could win money the participants, but during the auctions, where is fundamental element to wager more than the other, upon losing the play intensified the operation of the complex called stratum located under the cerebral cortex. 
This zone of the brain, besides many other functions, plays a role in the mechanism of "car prize" of the nervous system. 
Thus according to the scientists, the increase of the bets is explained like a prevention for cause not an intense reaction of the stratum. 
To support its theory, the economists of the scientific group carried out also a study of financial monitoring. 
In this experiment three groups wagered against a person in different circumstances. 
To the control group simply communicated him themselves the real value of the product in question, and its members wagered. 
To another group besides it him was promised that if they win, they would receive 15 dollars more than prize. 
On the other hand, the third group received exactly 15 dollars before the auction, but in case to lose the auction the members of the group lost even that money. 
Thus the only difference between the two groups was that for one stood out itself the triumph and for the other the failure. 
Nevertheless, verifying the hypothesis of the neurologists, the members of the group that played "against the failure" were willing to wager even more than the members of the control group and of the group "winning". 
"These results cannot be deduced of any existing economic theory previously. 
Therefore those up to now they explained the phenomena of the auctions only with the happiness to win and with the prevention of the risks. 
Only the visual neurological methods helped to resolve this contradiction between the two theories, so that now we arrive at a third explanation" - established Andrew Schotter, professor of the faculty of economy of the University of new York. 
Hepatitis: When should go the doctor? 
In the world some five hundred million people suffer of hepatitis B or C chronic, and in Hungary the chronic illness of the liver is considered one of the main causes of the death. 
It is calculated in a hundred thousand the number of infected in this country, but only seven thousand receive processing therefore many of the sick do not know that they are infected. 
The denomination of hepatitis is the common name of different illnesses of the liver caused by virus. 
The symptoms seem a lot; are characteristic the infection of the liver and the jaundice, but its pathogenic agents and the caused illnesses are very different. 
The virus of the hepatitis in dependence of the pathogenic agent spread by means of two main forms: the hepatitis TO and AND by eating way (for example with water or food infected), the hepatitis B, C, D and other virus with the blood and with corporal humors (sperm, humor of the vagina, saliva). 
It is recommendable to the travelers to be protected by means of vaccinates against the virus TO and B, against the C not vaccines exist. 
The symptoms of the hepatitis TO appear two or three weeks after consuming the food infected, is declared through a badly general state, weakness, abdominal pain and queasiness. 
After it they appear in the skin and in the white one of the eyes the jaundice, the excrement is put clearly, the urine of dark color and the healing can last even two - three weeks. 
Yearly a million people die in the world in cancer and liver cirrhosis caused by the hepatitis B, the most serious forms of this illness. 
The main reason of it is that according to the calculations, only one of each ten infected receives pharmacological processing. 
The hepatitis C can also have very serious consequences: without processing can produce liver cirrhosis and even cancer. 
The majority of them infected does not know that is sick because this pathological agent destroys in gradual form the cells of the liver and many times the first symptoms only appear 20-30 years later. 
Therefore is very important the premature recognition, the systematic medical control. 
It is a lot more frequent this illness in three groups: the people that had blood transfusion before 1991, the drug users and the ones that carry tattooings. 
Currently there are some 200 million people in the world that suffer of hepatitis C chronic. 
As to this illness can be discovered with a routine control of laboratory also, is worthwhile to consult with the doctor of the family upon experiencing some unknown symptom. 
The illness has healing if is discovered to time, is possible to exterminate the virus of the agency, thus the contagion can be suppressed and to prevent the cancer. 
September 30 is the World Day of the Hepatitis, which was organized for the first time in 2004 by organizations representatives of the sick. 
Its objective is to call the attention to the causes of the chronic infections of the liver caused by the virus and to the importance of its premature recognition. 
